_______________________________________________________________
HTML and CSS
_______________________________________________________________
##Code Example:
_______________________________________________________________
<!DOCTYPE html>                                                             
<html>                                                                      
  <head>                                                                    
    <title>Hello World</title>                                              
  </head>                                                                   
  <body>                                                                    
    <h1>Hello, World!</h1>                                                  
    <p>Welcome to learning HTML!</p>                                        
  </body>                                                                   
</html>                                                                     
_______________________________________________________________
###Indication Software:
_______________________________________________________________
Visual Studio Code: Lightweight and powerful editor.
Sublime Text: Lightweight alternative.
Any modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge) to preview HTML/CSS.

_______________________________________________________________
####Free Study Resources (English):
__________________________________________________________________________
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML: Official documentation.
freeCodeCamp: Practical HTML and CSS course.

